Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.94,0:00:04.98,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,She's a pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.36,0:00:07.40,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,...big person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.01,0:00:09.61,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:12.76,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Sky Priestess Farine, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:16.09,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. No problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:53.05,DogDays-ep-title,F,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}The Sky Priestess \Nand the Star People
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:50.31,DogDays-main-top,F,0000,0000,0000,,You're from the surface, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:52.60,DogDays-main-top,F,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:55.42,DogDays-main-top,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to put some
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:58.68,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,tea on and chat, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:02.43,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little busy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:04.16,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:08.31,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Pega said something might've happened \Nto you and the Star Whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:09.77,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:12.06,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Priestess, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.37,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:30.57,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, the Star Whale is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:32.67,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,battling an illness right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:36.25,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,When it gets sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:39.20,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,the foul air within it comes together and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:41.56,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,appears in this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:45.16,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,We call them Sickness Demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:48.48,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,They makes the Star Whale feel unwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:51.02,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,If the Sickness Demons overflow from
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.50,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,within its body, they may bring disaster to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:57.13,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,the Sky Sea Islands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:03:00.58,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and even the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.38,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:05.20,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:08.40,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,What will cure the Star Whale's illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:11.21,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The Star Whale loves songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:13.79,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The songs of the Star People
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:16.58,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,increase its self-healing powers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:19.84,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and allow it to maintain its health.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.34,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,The Star People?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.28,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a country of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.97,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,people living inside the Star Whale, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:28.21,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Aria, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:32.19,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I think the girl the prince saved \Nwas one of the Star People.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:35.83,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed a little strange \Nfor that, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:37.56,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Aria?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:40.21,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You know Aria?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:41.50,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:45.07,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,One of our friends found \Nher when she was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:49.11,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Her legs seemed to be a little funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:52.88,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,And she didn't remember why she was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:54.75,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:57.71,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:00.77,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,She's with a group that's somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:04.09,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,They're looking for the Fire \NDragon, since it got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.98,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The Fire Dragon...  Them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:11.48,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,They've gotten big enough to fly \Nwhile carrying people, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:14.40,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find them and bring them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:18.38,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You guests from the surface, \Nplease go to the Star People.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:21.36,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk more there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.66,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:36.52,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,One of my avatars will guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:38.88,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:42.44,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You go to get Sharl's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:45.23,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You go look for the Fire Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:46.75,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:48.96,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,This is Guri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:50.12,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Be good to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.39,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:02.65,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Aria-san, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:04.71,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.61,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:07.97,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:11.09,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,My head just hurts a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:14.60,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody! We got a message \Nfrom Shinku's group!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:17.70,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We need to gather up because \Nsomeone's coming to get us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:19.46,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:22.50,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find a place to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.86,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang in there 'til we can regroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.20,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,The priestess
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:32.30,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,is really big, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.39,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:37.39,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a servant of the surface land gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:41.41,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the same position \Nas that fox girl there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:44.19,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:47.20,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago I decided to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:50.20,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,live with the Star Whale,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.10,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and took the job of priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:56.96,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Every day is so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:01.46,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Using the water mirror I can see \Nall around the Star Whale's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:05.98,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and outside, and even the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:07.45,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:09.97,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,It's just up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:22.27,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,This is the village of the star people,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:24.18,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,blessed by the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.50,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're heading down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:32.48,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Priestess, jumping down from here \Nwill be a little difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.47,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.10,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:37.43,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,We'll carry you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.46,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,That statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:50.33,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like the star \Npeople in the fairy tales!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:51.57,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:54.83,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,This is a statue of the \Nfirst ruler of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:56.47,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The star people can
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:59.52,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,breathe in water and on land,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:02.30,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and swim faster than fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.86,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Like mermaids on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.19,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.43,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,But right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:12.67,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:14.84,DogDays-main,Me,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:17.05,DogDays-main,Me,0000,0000,0000,,That's the priestess and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:19.49,DogDays-main,Me,0000,0000,0000,,People from the surface?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:22.02,DogDays-main,Me,0000,0000,0000,,And people I've seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.79,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody! Priestess Farine is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:28.38,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk with you, \Nthe Dragon Priestess,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.30,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and the people from the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:38.18,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.81,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,You all look sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:43.84,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,They were hurt by the \Nsickness demons, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:45.17,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:48.24,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,When the sickness demons possess \Nyou, this is what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:51.12,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Headaches, fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:52.85,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,muscle aches, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:56.72,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The pain in your throat is really bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.86,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:01.08,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,can't talk at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:03.50,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,This is the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:09.84,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing better than most people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:12.52,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,In the water, there are a lot more...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:14.84,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,They're all suffering from illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:18.47,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Some people can't even get out of bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:21.60,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And Aria is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:23.61,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:26.86,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:29.61,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:31.54,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:34.18,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami! Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:35.63,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,What's that boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:38.62,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,One of my secret items.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:43.45,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. We've got a sick person here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:45.62,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any place she can rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:46.82,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:48.63,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aria?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:50.70,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:53.62,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she with these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.38,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Aria!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:57.51,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,What, you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:01.45,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Know her? She lives here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:04.65,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And she's our songstress!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:07.52,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,She's the most important \Nperson in the Star Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:10.27,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,She went missing two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.90,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,We were worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:15.19,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,From talking to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:18.03,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,it seemed like she doesn't remember anything
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:20.70,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,except her own name and the Sickness Demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.96,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,And more than anything, she can't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:24.59,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.93,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad Aria's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:31.38,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why this happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:35.44,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure if the sickness \Nis cured, she'll get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:40.05,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The Star Whale swallows many things,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:43.58,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,especially poisonous air, air which \Ncontains bad things in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:46.93,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The Star Whale swallows it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:48.81,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and purifies it inside its body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:53.15,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The Star Whale purifies the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:57.86,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I listen to its voice and the star people
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.61,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,sing festival songs and song of healing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:03.16,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,to maintain its health
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:06.29,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and keep the insides of its body bountiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.98,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,This place is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.80,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,usually much prettier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:13.98,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,It's not this dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:17.58,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,There have been Sickness Demons in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:21.16,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,but when the people and the Songstress sang,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:22.72,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,they got better immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:25.11,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:28.44,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,most of the Star People can't sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:31.70,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And the songstress lost her voice and memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:32.94,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,and is like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.35,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The Star Whale is suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.47,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can barely hear its voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.99,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:47.33,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Would it help if we got rid \Nof these Sickness Demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:52.99,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The Sickness Demons are born from \Nwithin the Star Whale's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:55.61,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,It would help if we could \Nreduce their numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:58.98,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,but that wouldn't really solve the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:03.05,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Um, can I ask something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.29,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:06.48,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have to be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:09.23,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,someone special who sings that song?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.75,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:14.44,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Someone with a wonderful, \Nkind, warm voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:17.24,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And they need to be a great singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.32,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Then um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:23.50,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I happen to know somebody like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.14,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:28.67,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,There are people on the surface \Nwho can sing, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:29.83,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.56,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And she's a star who's known worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:36.99,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:38.90,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,bring a video playback device!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:41.28,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered why you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:43.74,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,had that in your toolbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:45.35,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Rico.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:49.13,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,The princess's songs are an
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:50.82,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,important part of Biscotti's culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:54.97,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to introduce everyone \Nin the Sky Sea to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.01,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,All set!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:02.66,DogDays-main-top,B,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know dreams will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:06.70,DogDays-main-top,B,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wishes overflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:10.06,DogDays-main-top,B,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's grab hold of them now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:14.35,DogDays-main-top,B,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}inside the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:15.82,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:17.81,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice song.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:22.89,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:29.23,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I feel better!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:32.44,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The fever and tiredness are better!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:36.75,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:38.77,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I can speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:47.62,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Um... can I let everybody else hear this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.51,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.49,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:53.61,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:56.77,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,could sing the song of the Star Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:07.44,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Shinku and I will go get the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:09.69,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use the double hero express to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:11.93,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,bring her back at the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:13.72,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:15.64,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:18.68,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Priestess, please show us the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:19.52,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:23.19,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.78,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:29.12,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, what do we do until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:32.13,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,This place is safe for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:36.17,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should cut down on the \Nnumber of Sickness Demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:40.30,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I think my main body is summoning \Nthe large Sickness Demons
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:42.42,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and defeating them, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:46.26,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,if you can help, that would be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:47.68,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:48.76,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:51.20,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Rico can be our communications HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:53.39,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with Aria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:55.02,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.90,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Can Sharl and the vanguard stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:01.65,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens, I'd be worried \Nif it was just the chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.48,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:04.65,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:10.28,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I want to kick the crap out \Nof a big one with our team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:11.64,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:16.16,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let things get \Nhard for the girl team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:19.82,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think we \Nneed to worry about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.68,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,They know how to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:23.67,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:26.04,DogDays-internal,G,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:29.40,DogDays-internal,G,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Aria...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:33.27,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Gaul-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:35.43,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,was really concerned about Aria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:37.84,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:41.41,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Part of it may be that she saved him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:44.32,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because Aria-san's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:45.82,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:48.63,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,That may be Gaul-sama's type.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:49.68,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:54.70,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe Gaul's going to \Nfind love after Leo-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:56.96,DogDays-main,No,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder about Leo-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:15:00.85,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I think she does like Leaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:03.22,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul-sama, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:06.02,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,We're his childhood friends and bodyguards,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:08.93,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,so as for who'll be his wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:10.88,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're very interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:14.77,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think it'll be one of you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:16.29,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:17.92,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:20.02,DogDays-main,No,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:23.02,DogDays-main,No,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's not love or romance...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:26.28,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,We're connected by a different bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:29.24,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,A very strong bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:32.11,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You mean as a prince and his bodyguards?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:36.48,DogDays-main,No,0000,0000,0000,,As his childhood friends \Nwho've always been with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:39.89,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,We're basically siblings now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:44.63,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,To me you all are fun \Nlittle brothers and sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:46.19,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:54.38,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:55.59,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:57.26,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,...and do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:15:59.17,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:03.17,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:03.95,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:09.92,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The Star Whale is opening \Nits mouth right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.01,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:14.91,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,The outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:19.41,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'll follow you to the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.14,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:23.40,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,First we need to contact the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:26.17,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,And ask Cou-sama for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:33.65,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened to Aria-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:35.38,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:37.22,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like she's in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:41.78,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I brought medicine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:44.98,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it's okay \Nto use on people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.31,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:48.48,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Just the thought is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:51.01,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Aria always watched
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:53.48,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,the people on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:57.18,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,She always watched the surface \Npeople with the water mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.81,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,War games, did you call them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:01.37,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The ones that are like festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:03.68,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We do them a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:06.22,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,She liked those especially.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:10.05,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wanted to go \Nto the surface someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:13.89,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,We laughed and said it \Nwas impossible, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:16.32,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:20.65,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all land down there, \Nwith not a lot of water, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:24.02,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,They say that the most common \Nwater is salt water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.93,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:28.76,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get too far
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:31.52,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,from pure fresh water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:35.40,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use surface technology to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:38.82,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,For example, we could get a big carriage
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:42.82,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,and use either a box or half-sphere \Nfilled with fresh water...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:44.41,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Like this... like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:47.04,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:50.47,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You could make these in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:53.01,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,a lot of sizes depending on \Nhow many people were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.54,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,There are technologies we could use to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:58.83,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,purify the water and \Nmaintain its temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:17:59.68,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:03.83,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The Star People could use \Nthis to visit the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:05.31,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.61,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:09.07,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Aria will be so \Nhappy when she hears it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:13.44,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,We should have started talking to the \Npeople on the surface sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:15.14,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,The surface people
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:18.05,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,can't come to the Sky Sea easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:21.21,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We were only able to do it \Nthanks to the Fire Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:23.45,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones who could get up here easily
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:27.33,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,are the Heroes of the various \Ncountries or the leaders
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.71,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,who have treasure swords that let you fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.46,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, the last person
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.71,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,to come here was a Hero, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.30,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.80,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The hero Adel and her party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:45.37,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Her signature's on display \Nin my great-grandma's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:47.81,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the Hero Adel-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.53,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Not only do we know her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:51.25,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,she told us
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:54.19,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,her story yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:57.69,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,She's still alive! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:19:00.04,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,She's still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:01.69,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And I was
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:05.00,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,raised by a member of her party.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:10.46,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,The sky and the surface really \Nare connected, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:11.83,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.30,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:18.40,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:20.64,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,but I think I've seen \Nthem somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:23.36,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Aria...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:26.85,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Something's strange about them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.91,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:31.23,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Is it one of Aria-dono's acquaintances?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:36.05,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.48,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Farine-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:47.62,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.37,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:12.19,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,This is... Sickness Demon poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:15.52,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Give back Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:23.25,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:25.53,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Get the priestess and Aria somewhere safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:27.09,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:35.22,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Senka Reppuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.06,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.30,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Fox girl... priestess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:49.57,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Seal evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:52.06,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:11.78,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:14.56,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Aria...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:16.72,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Our promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:21.06,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Verde?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:24.01,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:32.39,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:35.17,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,a strange sound from the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:36.13,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:44.86,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Aria...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:49.99,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Aria. Our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:53.50,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hear your song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.47,0:21:56.04,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Only me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:58.92,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Verde.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:33.18,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Aria's songs belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.18,0:23:35.22,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,They belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:36.45,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, Aria!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:37.63,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:40.05,DogDays-next-ep-title,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}Song of the Stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:39.68,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,...you watch next time.
